{"tid":1564134,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[頹又半途而廢系列] 此路不通--沙螺灣","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T16:20:54.000Z","uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d447b3f59636604a9baf4961087e3d99ff1c2c69","tid":1564134,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"夏日炎炎，少年帶著他那便宜的單車走上了一條不歸路"},{"pid":"0c53275d5b91108375920444942c6250e06143c9","tid":1564134,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6e10c8e243c33cc48b147e971323052c5780a748","tid":1564134,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8030943850404ad046dd5ae2e6cdd6fe23a54f2a","tid":1564134,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5803e28cf59378c31152cc0cf71207860ecdbf73","tid":1564134,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"烈日當空，一身輕裝的少年歡快地乘著單車前往未知的旅途<br />\n窄路遇上同路人，大家或慢下來或一時停頓禮讓對方<br />\n上坡路斜而力有不&quot;&quot;第&quot;&quot;，惟有運用全身氣力踩踏並左右擺動單車前進<br />\n可惜有時仍是無法敵過那坡度，於是無奈地一步步推著單車跨越那短又&quot;&quot;豆&quot;&quot;的小斜路"},{"pid":"ed0310ec54fb821653c4b79dee87126f0a37d2ac","tid":1564134,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:25:01.000Z","msg":"現時我們不&quot;&quot;搵&quot;&quot;許所有未授權人士通過或進入我們村，請回"},{"pid":"c0847d800ba5c21e6c9fc7f2014cf066f665f260","tid":1564134,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"那邊可能有路能走出這地方，儘管嘗試一下吧"},{"pid":"b930f579cf74e955f2defc80b81d9c96a4b45299","tid":1564134,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"不不<br />\n金屬銀色的16寸摺疊單車，摺疊相關的結構簡陋而摺疊過程也費時<br />\n前輪剎車只是一個「C」字或可稱為馬蹄型，後輪的是鼓剎，整套制動系統的整體評價就是平價平地平淡<br />\n減速的時候需要前後兩者並用，伴隨著劣質剎車部件導致的刺耳噪音，車子總算是可以慢下來<br />\n但在落斜時只能期望車速不會快，慢或者停車就過於困難了"},{"pid":"edf784b864af51e173317eefdd8c67525e83775d","tid":1564134,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"工口漫會有看完的一天嗎?不存在的"},{"pid":"c08e4453af54bd87dd12f7a6b943b66a3d409c75","tid":1564134,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"唔記得用不推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}